{"tid":426807,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗批評噓國歌行為　憂令港足被罰","createTime":"2017-10-07T03:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T05:00:16.000Z","uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4aeeda3fbcbf4eb352954ba5527354353521241f","tid":426807,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:36:04.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗認為，有球迷在前晚港足友誼賽奏國歌期間發出噓聲，行為不能接受，強調國歌和國旗是國家象徵，是嚴肅的標誌，一定要尊重。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗希望之後港足對馬來西亞的賽事，不會再有同類情況發生，他說，若令到港足的賽事從此要閉門作賽，對球迷不是好事，對香港形象亦造成好大損害，呼籲球迷和公眾好好反思。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗表示，國歌法是全國性法律，可以根據《基本法》納入《基本法》附件三，但立法需時，特區政府會按照香港憲制和法律制度，完成法律諮詢和草擬工作後，在適當時候進行本地立法。<br />\n<br />\n被問到基本法委員會委員饒戈平認為，應研究國歌法能否有追溯力，張建宗表示，要留待律政司再研究。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1357735-20171007.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1357735-20171007.htm&d=SUUlpUkacCygxzKbGvHTM0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=52241e1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1357735-20171007.htm&h=abe92704\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1357735-20171007.htm</a>"},{"pid":"eda3a611edab755bbc3c35226fc7de6ba7a3bc74","tid":426807,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"一有機會即刻撲出嚟舔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca819aa64ebef8fef03ef2a5ab61d66aee15e2ff","tid":426807,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一有機會即刻撲出嚟舔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下屆想做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4877485e0df3b9df53fff0251ec4e5060d053d7","tid":426807,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\"